    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring an 11.5:1 compression ratio and six individual throttle bodies for instantaneous transient response. This example boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a refreshed double-VANOS system, ensuring the variable valve timing operates at peak efficiency across the 8,000 RPM powerband. Power is delivered through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. With its original factory finish and a chassis free of bushing compliance, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity to own a mechanically flawless icon.",
