      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offering a truly exceptional 2021 BMW M340i in Mineral White Metallic over Tacora Red leather. This vehicle has been maintained to a standard that exceeds factory requirements. The exterior paint is in showroom condition, having been treated with a multi-stage paint correction and a premium 5-year ceramic coating immediately upon delivery. There are zero rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks. The 19-inch M-Double spoke wheels are pristine with no curb rash, wrapped in Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires with 90% tread remaining. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the leather remains matte and supple, the 'new car' scent is still present, and the glass and trim are free of any micro-scratches. Mechanically, this car is perfect, with all maintenance performed exclusively at the BMW dealership every 5,000 miles. It has been strictly garaged in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen rain or snow. This is a collector-grade example for a buyer who refuses to compromise on quality.",
